<table width="100%" border=0 cellpadding=3 cellspacing=3 align="center">	
	<tr><td>Please follow the steps below in order to remove the header and footer of the page.<br><br></td></tr>
	<tr><td><UL>
			<li> - On the letter click on "FILE" then go to "PAGE SETUP"<br><br></li>
			<li> - Remove all information for header and footer as shown below:<br><br>
				<img src="../pics/setup.jpg" border="0"><br><br>
			</li>
			<li> - Click on OK and print the letter.<br><br></li>
			</UL>
		</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td>Your browser will save this information therefore you do not need to do this everytime you wish to print a letter<br><br></td></tr>
	<tr>
		<td>If you wish to have you header and footer back just put the header and footer information back to the page setup as shown below.<br><br></td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td><UL>
			<li> - On the letter click on "FILE" then go to "PAGE SETUP"<br><br></li>
			<li> - Copy all the header and footer information back as shown below:<br><br>
				<img src="../pics/headerfooter.gif" border="0"><br><br>
			</li>
			<li> - Click on OK.<br><br></li>
			</UL>
		</td>
	</tr>
	
